        Caveat on Property in Queensland: What It Means for Sellers and How to Remove It
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        A caveat on your title can stop a sale before it starts. Here is what Queensland sellers need to know about caveats, why they appear, and what the removal process actually involves.
      </p>
